{"tid":1358494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無一d 比較for 廢中廢老d 既文宣材料？","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T06:24:16.000Z","uid":35003,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"602ffb25f6f8eb607f00d68f590f0e68810389e0","tid":1358494,"uid":35003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:45:08.000Z","msg":"我同朋友想幫手出街做下社區文宣。但就咁scan 過下d 文宣都係比較年青一d 既style ，唔係好入到屋。<br />\n<br />\n想問會唔會有d 廢中廢老style d，以元朗事件為切入點，強調到下面三樣野既文宣材料可以畀我地去print？<br />\n<br />\n1）警黑<strong>明顯</strong>合作<br />\n2）警察不再盡力保障市民安全<br />\n3）市民無所依靠 只能靠自組社區自衛組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701cbfeb5c8383bcaca0c7ca25fa34ca94c63217","tid":1358494,"uid":113342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:47:57.000Z","msg":"深藍唔會睇你d野<br />\n睇完都會自我Filter走佢唔想睇既訊息<br />\n就好似你睇大公，東方一樣"},{"pid":"f0e612f1998d81553287934e42151a713fd6e6bb","tid":1358494,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"9fa23a8cea2aab00225a1f85bbde0e92c71c5fbe","tid":1358494,"uid":